# Marketing product (locked)

Personal **portfolio / showcase** site for Yehuda Huri (Senior Full Stack Engineer & System
Designer) — **not** a freelance/consulting sales site and **not** a generic dev-portfolio clone.
No "hire me", pricing, services, or "happy clients" framing.

## Landing structure (single page)

Section order in `LandingPage.tsx` (hashes in `LANDING_SECTIONS` / `routes.ts`):

1. **overview** — hero + single "View my work" CTA + 3 feature/value cards (expertise, products, open source)
2. **about**
3. **experience** — selected credibility (Amdocs, Harmony 2.0, side products); **not** a year-by-year timeline
4. **skills**
5. **portfolio**

There are **no** `services`, `howIWork`, `faq`, or `contact` sections (removed with the freelance framing).
Legal pages are separate routes: `/privacy`, `/accessibility` (not landing sections).

## Portfolio

- Structural data (URLs, tags, image paths): `frontend/src/config/marketing/portfolioProjects.ts`
- Copy (problem / solution / outcome): i18n `marketing.portfolio.{key}.*` in **both** locale files
- Keys list: `PORTFOLIO_PROJECT_KEYS` in `contentKeys.ts`
- Link keys: `live`, `video`, `github`, `npm`, `docs`, `store` (order in `PORTFOLIO_LINK_ORDER`,
  labels in `marketing.portfolio.links.*`)
- Screenshots: `frontend/public/portfolio/` (`.webp`/`.jpg`, ~1280×720); `placeholder.svg` OK until real shots exist
- Current set (unless user changes): **Ateret Yosef**, **cursor-chat-bridge**, **DevToolsHub**, **Harmony 2.0**.
  cursor-chat-bridge uses YouTube demo thumbnails (`cursor-chat-bridge-1/2.jpg`) + a `video` link.

## Contact & social

- **No contact form / no contact section** — removed. Visitors reach out via social links only.
- Social URLs: single source `frontend/src/config/constants/social.ts` — LinkedIn, GitHub, npm (no X/Twitter);
  rendered by `SocialLinks` in the footer.
- Contact email `udah10@gmail.com` appears only in the privacy/accessibility legal copy.
- No phone number on site; calendar booking **out of scope** unless explicitly requested

## Legal & compliance

- Pages: Privacy Policy + Accessibility Statement only (no Terms unless user asks)
- Content authority: [`docs/LEGAL_PAGES_SPEC.md`](mdc:docs/LEGAL_PAGES_SPEC.md); i18n namespace `legal.*`
- Update privacy policy if analytics or new data collection is added
- Cookie banner: **not** required until cookie-based analytics/ads are enabled

## SEO & analytics

- Meta/OG: `SeoHead` + `react-helmet-async`; OG image `frontend/public/og-image.webp` (1200×630)
- `robots.txt` / `sitemap.xml`: replace `YOUR_DOMAIN` at go-live — see launch checklist
- Analytics: **deferred by default** (`VITE_ANALYTICS_PROVIDER=none`); prefer Cloudflare Web Analytics when enabled

## Explicit out of scope (unless user asks)

Blog, newsletter signup, phone number on site, testimonials section, client carousel, generic skill
bars / percentage charts, freelance/services/pricing framing, backend/auth/dashboard, Formspree/backend
SES contact unless user switches intentionally.

